init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Will it be "#1 Dad" or will it be "#10 Dad"?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As you are sitting there, you suddenly realize what might ease his pain.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He seems to have forgotten all about the mug, and is focused on what you are saying.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You notice that he is no longer even looking into space, but is now listening and responding to your stories.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There is a huge mug with "#1 Dad" written on it.
